# MusicCatalogSearchResponse.TopResult

**Enumeration**

An item that represents one of the top results in a catalog search response.

## Declaration

```swift
enum TopResult
```

## Enumeration Cases

- **MusicCatalogSearchResponse.TopResult.album(_:)**: An item that corresponds to an album.
- **MusicCatalogSearchResponse.TopResult.artist(_:)**: An item that corresponds to an artist.
- **MusicCatalogSearchResponse.TopResult.curator(_:)**: An item that corresponds to a curator.
- **MusicCatalogSearchResponse.TopResult.musicVideo(_:)**: An item that corresponds to a music video.
- **MusicCatalogSearchResponse.TopResult.playlist(_:)**: An item that corresponds to a playlist.
- **MusicCatalogSearchResponse.TopResult.radioShow(_:)**: An item that corresponds to a radio show.
- **MusicCatalogSearchResponse.TopResult.recordLabel(_:)**: An item that corresponds to a record label.
- **MusicCatalogSearchResponse.TopResult.song(_:)**: An item that corresponds to a song.
- **MusicCatalogSearchResponse.TopResult.station(_:)**: An item that corresponds to a station.

## Instance Properties

- **artwork**: The artwork of this top result for catalog search.
- **id**: The unique identifier of this top result for catalog search.
- **title**: The title of this top result for catalog search.
